<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I said above that there are some compliance is=
sues with that button, but that is the real=C2=A0beauty of this idea:</p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Elon Musk generally seems a bit aggre=
ssive on compliance matters, and in particular he does not care at all abou=
t securities law compliance. =E2=80=9CI want to be clear. I do not respect =
the SEC. I do not respect them,=E2=80=9D <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloom=
bergbusiness.com/click/31156532.260450/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9v=
cGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMTktMDItMjYvZWxvbi1tdXNrLWtlZXBzLXR3ZWV0aW5nP2NtcGl=
