=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bord=
er-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: so=
lid; background-color: #ccc;">  enforce securities laws</a> against Musk?</=
li>
</ol>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I think a lot of people could offer a more sea=
mless and convenient retail stock trading experience if they did not care a=
bout, and were not subject to,=C2=A0securities regulation.<a class=3D"footn=
ote-index" href=3D"#footnote-3" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: n=
one !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; bor=
der-bottom-style: none !important; background-color: transparent !important=
; display: inline-block;">
<span>[3]</span>
</a>=C2=A0Why not Twitter?</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Also, everything I said above, but 10 times mo=
re so, for trading=C2=A0<em>crypto=C2=A0</em>on Twitter. As is true for a l=
ot of people on Twitter, <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com=
